<main class="site-main">
  <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
    <div class="identity">
      <%= image_tag "avatar.png", class: "avatar", alt: "抽象个人头像" %>
      <div class="identity__copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Software Engineer / Backend Developer</p>
        <h1 id="intro-title">Zuogh</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">软件工程师，专注后端开发，喜欢把复杂业务做成清晰、稳定、可维护的系统。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="intro-copy">
      <p>
        我熟悉后端服务、API 设计、数据库建模、异步任务和系统稳定性建设。主要使用
        <strong>Ruby</strong>、<strong>Rails</strong>、<strong>Golang</strong> 等技术栈，
        也会关注工程效率、测试策略和线上问题排查。
      </p>
      <p>
        这个站点会持续整理我的技术文章、项目实践和工作流记录。你可以在这里看到我如何拆解需求、
        设计服务边界、权衡 Rails 与 Go 的使用场景，以及如何把后端系统打磨得更可靠。
      </p>
    </div>

    <nav class="social-links" aria-label="社交链接">
      <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">X</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a>
    </nav>
  </section>

  <%= link_to games_path, class: "feature-link" do %>
    <span class="feature-link__content">
      <span class="feature-link__label">Bored? Play some games</span>
      <span class="feature-link__text">Rails + Stimulus 做的一些终端小游戏。工作卡住时，来敲几下键盘。</span>
    </span>
    <span class="feature-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span>
  <% end %>

  <%= link_to photos_path, class: "feature-link feature-link--photos" do %>
    <span class="feature-link__content">
      <span class="feature-link__label">Photo log</span>
      <span class="feature-link__text">记录一些城市、旅行和工作间隙里的画面。</span>
    </span>
    <span class="feature-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span>
  <% end %>

  <%= link_to tools_path, class: "feature-link feature-link--tools" do %>
    <span class="feature-link__content">
      <span class="feature-link__label">Tools for actual work</span>
      <span class="feature-link__text">放一些我自己也会用的小工具。第一站是浏览器内图片尺寸调整，后面会继续补充。</span>
    </span>
    <span class="feature-link__arrow" aria-hidden="true">-&gt;</span>
  <% end %>

  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="writing-title">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2 id="writing-title">近期写作</h2>
      <%= link_to "View all", posts_path %>
    </div>

    <div class="list">
      <% @recent_posts.each do |post| %>
        <%= link_to post_path(post), class: "list-item" do %>
          <span>
            <strong><%= post.title %></strong>
            <% if post.excerpt.present? %>
              <small><%= post.excerpt %></small>
            <% end %>
          </span>
          <time datetime="<%= post.display_date&.to_date&.iso8601 %>"><%= post_month(post) %></time>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="projects" aria-labelledby="projects-title">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2 id="projects-title">项目</h2>
      <a href="mailto:hello@example.com?subject=Project">聊聊合作</a>
    </div>

    <div class="projects">
      <a class="project" href="#">
        <strong>Rails Service Notes</strong>
        <span>整理 Rails 后端服务设计、Active Record 建模和后台任务实践。</span>
      </a>
      <a class="project" href="#">
        <strong>Go Backend Lab</strong>
        <span>记录 Golang 服务、并发控制、超时处理和接口性能优化实验。</span>
      </a>
      <a class="project" href="#">
        <strong>Ops Checklist</strong>
        <span>沉淀部署、监控、日志、告警和线上故障排查的检查清单。</span>
      </a>
      <a class="project" href="#">
        <strong>Backend Toolbox</strong>
        <span>积累给自己和团队复用的脚本、调试工具和开发者效率工具。</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section stack-section" aria-labelledby="stack-title">
    <div class="section__header">
      <h2 id="stack-title">现在关注</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="stack">
      <span>Ruby</span>
      <span>Ruby on Rails</span>
      <span>Golang</span>
      <span>PostgreSQL</span>
      <span>API Design</span>
      <span>Background Jobs</span>
      <span>Observability</span>
      <span>System Design</span>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-mark" aria-hidden="true">ZGH</div>
  <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="页脚链接">
    <a href="#intro-title">About</a>
    <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
    <%= link_to "Writing", posts_path %>
    <%= link_to "Photos", photos_path %>
    <%= link_to "Tools", tools_path %>
    <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a>
  </nav>
</footer>
